metadata.description:
NFT'S in this collection are given free of charge to the Crypto Stars Collection holders and early supporters of the project. They can decide to hodl, gift or sell them.

Those animated rewards are not part of the 333 Collection.

Collection minted on 28.11.2022 
Total Supply 333

Available here:  
https://rarible.com/the-crypto-stars-collection/items


The Crypo Stars Limited Edition is designed to reward members of our family and offers upcoming secret drops. 

Only true followers of my work will get these items.

Who ever owns any of these on their wallet will get occasional exclusive drops to their wallet from me. 
Those rewards will be categorized by colors.
